            <title>[CXF-3505] CXF attachment doesn&apos;t compatible with SUN&apos;s  ACTIVATION library</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-3505</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;if using sun&apos;s javax.activation api (version 1.1) instead of geronimo&apos;s activation api. CXF&apos;s attachments . the http connection cannot be released corrrectly;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
